Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備著以電腦為導航系統的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:33.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:40.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:53.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:01:00.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:04.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:15.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:27.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:33.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:43.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:50.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高智能方程式世界盃錦標賽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將與世界各地舉行十場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每場的前六名將可獲得積分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並采累積分制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了一般的場地外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有市街 山嶽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠以及雪地等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種地形的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來考驗車子跟選手的極限
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠通過這些考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且得到最高分的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是世界最快的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一戰的結果是奈特·修馬赫第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅比第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人因為中途退場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而沒有得到分數
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二戰的比賽結果又將如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十五話  與少女的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣也稀薄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動口不如動手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經快沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一場長距離的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意速度的分配
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我一定不會中途退場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次比賽是通宵舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體力的保持是致勝的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 隼人你要多休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一閉上眼晴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次比賽中途退場的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會出現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是那麼的清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我沒辦法忘記它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武八 跟我來 我們也去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人的鬥志都顯得相當高昂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真像是一場盛大的聯歡會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是去年的冠軍賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅比的車迷們真熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也過去讓他簽個名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然會喜歡那種型的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比那些長不大的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有魅力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久我也會像他那樣神氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我簽名 幫我簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒練習過簽名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簽名…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條先生 請幫我簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽的時候要好好開車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會要一個在第一場比賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途退場車手的簽名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真謝謝你的指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是風見隼人對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次決賽的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在電視上看過你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退場的時候也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關你什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 算了 不要跟她說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是說不得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位差不多了在比賽之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直輝還有很多事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這歐巴桑是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直輝 該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的車迷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愈來愈不懂禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅比是在這一次的決賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得第二名的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我簽個名好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅比 老闆找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 今天到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特·修馬赫 上次決賽優勝者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 能不能幫我簽個名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我在趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 修馬赫他現在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何簽個名就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要囉唆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能怪我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:06:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫他硬是要叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修馬赫先生簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不需要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他動手動腳的太粗暴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他是忠實車迷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不應該是比賽之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來打擾選手的情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太沒禮貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是個賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不瞭解這個道埋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是本人啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請你幫我簽個名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我的簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簽的名很難看耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女兒就會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你不是霹靂車的車迷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡看車賽的是我女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫琳達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 她就在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿到了羅比的簽名了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我沒拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 奈特·修馬赫的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽前車手不喜歡車迷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾他們的情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳達 你應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位選手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是幫我簽了名了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個簽名好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做琳達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一戰失敗了沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要第二戰好好加油就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫武八
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣 武八
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要罵武八嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又不是武八的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有活力喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 我們去幫琳達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要選手們的簽名好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你不必為我們這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在對你而言時間是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟明日香比較容易接近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他選手拿到簽名的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你是怎麼搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳達曾經那樣的批評你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻還幫她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我不會在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我比較喜歡像她那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直話直說的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 麻煩你幫我簽一個名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了 那我就幫你簽名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我簽多少都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比賽前夕竟然會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向競爭對手要求簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時代真是變了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簽名 真是可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比賽前夕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道沒有別的事可做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多集中一點注意力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到這個地方來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是來聽你說教的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白原因就亂罵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不簽就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要給你一個忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽中要對艾迪利提高警覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他的駕駛方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的魯莽粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳達 我們也要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭還有積奇的簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高不高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩二位了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正離比賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好長一段時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼沒有奈特·修馬赫的簽名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連隼人也要不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修馬赫的簽名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道沒有跟他說明原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有說他就開口罵人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一氣之下我扭頭就走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他那麼多 誰理他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是你的態度不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那換我去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會替琳達要到簽名的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便證明隼人他沒有說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修馬赫 有人要見你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什麼事嗎 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你這麼忙的時候來打擾你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想拜託修馬赫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我簽個名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有個小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的忠實車迷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和隼人到底在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是車手和隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去應付比賽的重要時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼還會有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來要簽名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們也是車隊的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該要明白這個道理才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太多管閒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是我的什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你來教訓我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人他會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要幫助一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的小女孩來跟你要簽名的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可以這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分青紅皂白就責備他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不簽就算了嘛 有什麼了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 武八
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳達已經很久沒有這樣快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳達她是一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活潑開朗的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是琳達卻沒有勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用兩腳站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生已經斷定他兩腳已經
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全痊癒可以走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無論我勸多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總是不肯嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是琳達的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她能在生日的這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在現場看霹靂車比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該可以增加她的信心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我跟琳達一起去玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武八真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用自己的雙腳到處走動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳達 琳達 我們跟武八
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去跑步好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 武八
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武八 好棒 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只賽車連跑步都中途退出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到這次的決賽結束以後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會知道我的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不比羅比還有修馬赫差
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是很棒的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說大話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是跑完全程就夠你忙的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你光是饑笑別人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳明明已經治療好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還坐在輪椅上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真是個大嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 如果你能獲得前三名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就用我的兩腳走路給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前三名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你做不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我就答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把前三名的榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當做送給你的生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連生日的事都告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你有把握獲得前三名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾手指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾手指的意思就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果兩個人約定好要做某件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定要去達成才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 琳達伸出你的小指頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小指頭 勾手指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊的人就是小狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 小指頭勾手指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊的人是小狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界賽的第二戰秘魯之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開賽的時間愈來愈逼近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先為各位報告一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預賽的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名是超音速騎士修馬赫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二名是美國的積奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三名是巴西的羅比
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四名是法蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而新條直輝先生是第七名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大友是第l2名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最年輕的賽車手隼人他在l5名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏先為觀眾朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明比賽的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次比賽是采兩段制
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成前半段還有後半段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩段的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前半段是從這裏到福斯科
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到中間點的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各個隊伍的接引車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以先開到普諾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子在到達終點以後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以先進行準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而選手們也可以稍做休息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就進入後半段的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各隊選手必須奮力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶先到達拉巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括了中繼點的休息在內
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選手們必須獨自一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,度過整個夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以稱得上是一次殘酷的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽道路的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平均標高為3825公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣非常的稀薄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而各輛車子必須放置氧氣簡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以備之用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修馬赫先生要我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個送來給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們收下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是修馬赫先生的親筆簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修馬赫請人送了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的親筆簽名過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修馬赫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這麼做有什麼用意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正把簽名交給琳達好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修馬赫這傢伙真不乾脆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全日本錦標賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有辦法將阿斯拉達幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這次的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了報恩也為了實力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要讓你變成一堆廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位觀眾紅色的信號燈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經亮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在綠燈亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各車已經往前衝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次決賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘魯山嶽跑道之戰已經正式的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人的起跑還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達的狀況也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕快到中間點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快跟直升機取得連繫 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位觀眾再過不久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜就要降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣溫也將下降到零下25度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又髒又變化多端的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路延綿不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這奪命的比賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據過去三年來的統計
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑完全程的比率只有32％
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底那一位賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在今天的比賽裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過生死難關\N獲得最後的勝利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我做了那樣的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的可以達成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次我一定要你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬身在秘魯荒郊野外
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小指頭勾手指
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊的人就是小狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會遵守我們的約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人目光沒有在背後注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肩負著使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下雙手 仰望天空時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有現在加倍努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能有明天的輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 不用後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著自己樹立的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎著風前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我們會是勝利者

